<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ meta.title }}</title>
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ meta.title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ meta.description }}">
<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ meta.url }}">
<meta property="og:image" content="https://aisyncclub.github.io/moneyclub/og-image.jpg">
<meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
<meta property="og:image:height" content="630">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="AI싱크 재테크클럽">
<meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ meta.title }}">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ meta.twitter_description }}">
<meta name="twitter:image" content="https://aisyncclub.github.io/moneyclub/og-image.jpg">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:#0b0b0d; --s:#17171b; --s2:#1e1e24; --bd:#2a2a32;
  --t:#e4e4e7; --td:#8b8b96; --tm:#5c5c66;
  --up:#22c55e; --dn:#ef4444; --w:#eab308;
  --blue:#60a5fa; --purple:#a78bfa; --orange:#fb923c;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--t);line-height:1.7;min-height:100vh}
.ctr{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 80px}

.back-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--td);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:16px;padding:6px 12px;background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:6px}
.back-link:hover{color:var(--t);border-color:#555}

/* Article Header */
.art-meta{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.meta-date{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--td);font-weight:600}
.meta-badge{font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:700;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.15);color:var(--dn)}

h1.art-title{font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:12px}
.art-lead{font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--td);line-height:1.8;padding:14px 16px;background:var(--s);border-left:3px solid var(--dn);border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin-bottom:24px}

/* Dashboard */
.dash{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;margin:20px 0}
.dcard{background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:10px;padding:12px}
.dcard.up{border-color:rgba(34,197,94,0.3)}
.dcard.dn{border-color:rgba(239,68,68,0.3)}
.dcard.wr{border-color:rgba(234,179,8,0.3)}
.dc-label{font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--tm);margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase}
.dc-val{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff}
.dc-sub{font-size:0.68rem;margin-top:3px}
.dcard.up .dc-sub{color:var(--up)}
.dcard.dn .dc-sub{color:var(--dn)}
.dcard.wr .dc-sub{color:var(--w)}

/* Section */
.sec{margin:28px 0}
.sec h2{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.sec h2 .icon{margin-right:6px}
.sec p{font-size:0.87rem;color:var(--t);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:12px}
.sec p strong{color:#fff;font-weight:700}
.sec p .hl-up{color:var(--up);font-weight:600}
.sec p .hl-dn{color:var(--dn);font-weight:600}
.sec p .hl-wr{color:var(--w);font-weight:600}

/* Timeline */
.timeline{background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin:14px 0}
.tl-item{display:flex;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd)}
.tl-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.tl-date{flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--tm);width:60px;padding-top:2px}
.tl-body{flex:1}
.tl-title{font-size:0.84rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:2px}
.tl-desc{font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--td);line-height:1.7}
.tl-item.red .tl-date{color:var(--dn)}
.tl-item.green .tl-date{color:var(--up)}
.tl-item.yellow .tl-date{color:var(--w)}

/* Scenario cards */
.scenarios{display:grid;gap:10px;margin:14px 0}
.scn{background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;border-left:3px solid}
.scn.a{border-left-color:var(--up)}
.scn.b{border-left-color:var(--w)}
.scn.c{border-left-color:var(--dn)}
.scn-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:6px}
.scn-title{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff}
.scn-prob{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px}
.scn.a .scn-prob{background:rgba(34,197,94,0.15);color:var(--up)}
.scn.b .scn-prob{background:rgba(234,179,8,0.15);color:var(--w)}
.scn.c .scn-prob{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.15);color:var(--dn)}
.scn-desc{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--td);line-height:1.7}

/* Calendar */
.cal{background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:12px;padding:4px;margin:14px 0}
.cal-row{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:11px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd);align-items:center}
.cal-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.cal-day{flex-shrink:0;width:56px;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--tm)}
.cal-event{flex:1;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--td);line-height:1.5}
.cal-event strong{color:#fff}
.cal-row.star{background:rgba(234,179,8,0.05)}
.cal-row.star .cal-day{color:var(--w)}

/* Insights */
.insights{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(96,165,250,0.06),rgba(167,139,250,0.04));border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.15);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin:14px 0}
.insights h3{font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:10px}
.insight-item{padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.08);font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--t);line-height:1.7}
.insight-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.insight-item strong{color:var(--blue);font-weight:700}

/* Glossary helper */
.gloss-box{background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;margin:14px 0}
.gloss-box h3{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px}
.gloss-box .gloss-terms{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:8px 0 10px}
.gloss-term{font-size:0.72rem;padding:4px 10px;background:var(--s2);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:14px;color:var(--td)}
.gloss-link{display:inline-block;margin-top:6px;padding:9px 14px;background:rgba(96,165,250,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.3);border-radius:8px;color:var(--blue);font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}
.gloss-link:hover{background:rgba(96,165,250,0.15)}

/* Callout */
.callout{background:rgba(234,179,8,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(234,179,8,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin:14px 0}
.callout strong{color:var(--w)}
.callout.red{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.05);border-color:rgba(239,68,68,0.2)}
.callout.red strong{color:var(--dn)}
.callout.green{background:rgba(34,197,94,0.05);border-color:rgba(34,197,94,0.2)}
.callout.green strong{color:var(--up)}
.callout p{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--t);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:0}

/* Navigation footer */
.nav-footer{display:flex;gap:10px;margin:30px 0 16px}
.nav-btn{flex:1;padding:13px;text-align:center;background:var(--s);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:10px;color:var(--t);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;transition:all 0.15s}
.nav-btn:hover{border-color:#555;background:var(--s2)}
.nav-btn.primary{background:rgba(96,165,250,0.08);border-color:rgba(96,165,250,0.3);color:var(--blue)}

.footer{text-align:center;font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--tm);padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--bd);line-height:1.8;margin-top:20px}
.footer .disclaimer{padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.15);border-radius:8px;color:#c87a7a;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:0.72rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="ctr">

  <a class="back-link" href="index.html">← 재테크클럽</a>

  <div class="art-meta">
    <span class="meta-date">{{ article.date_label }}</span>
{% if article.is_urgent %}
    <span class="meta-badge">🚨 긴급 업데이트</span>
{% endif %}
  </div>

  <h1 class="art-title">{{ article.headline }}</h1>

  <div class="art-lead">
    <strong>한 줄 요약.</strong> {{ article.lead }}
  </div>

  <div class="dash">
{% for card in dashboard %}
    <div class="dcard {{ card.tone }}">
      <div class="dc-label">{{ card.label }}</div>
      <div class="dc-val">{{ card.value }}</div>
      <div class="dc-sub">{{ card.sub }}</div>
    </div>
{% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">📖</span>무슨 일이 있었나?</h2>
{% for paragraph in article.narrative %}
    <p>{{ paragraph|safe }}</p>
{% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">📅</span>{{ article.timeline_title }}</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
{% for item in article.timeline %}
      <div class="tl-item {{ item.color }}">
        <div class="tl-date">{{ item.date }}</div>
        <div class="tl-body">
          <div class="tl-title">{{ item.title }}</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">{{ item.desc }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">🤔</span>우리 자산에 어떤 영향?</h2>
{% for paragraph in article.asset_impact %}
    <p>{{ paragraph|safe }}</p>
{% endfor %}

    <div class="callout">
      <p><strong>⚡ 핵심 패턴:</strong> {{ article.asset_callout|safe }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">📌</span>이번 주 핵심 일정</h2>
    <div class="cal">
{% for event in article.calendar %}
      <div class="cal-row{% if event.star %} star{% endif %}">
        <div class="cal-day">{{ event.day }}</div>
        <div class="cal-event">{{ event.event|safe }}</div>
      </div>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
    <p>{{ article.calendar_takeaway|safe }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">🎯</span>3가지 시나리오</h2>

    <div class="scenarios">
{% for scn in article.scenarios %}
      <div class="scn {{ scn.tone }}">
        <div class="scn-head">
          <span class="scn-title">{{ scn.title }}</span>
          <span class="scn-prob">확률 {{ scn.probability }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="scn-desc">
          {{ scn.desc|replace('\n', '<br>\n          ')|safe }}
        </div>
      </div>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">💡</span>기억할 핵심 포인트</h2>
    <div class="insights">
      <h3>📌 오늘의 인사이트 5가지</h3>

{% for insight in article.insights %}
      <div class="insight-item">
        {{ insight|safe }}
      </div>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">📚</span>과거 유사 사건에서 배우기</h2>
{% for paragraph in article.historical_context %}
    <p>{{ paragraph|safe }}</p>
{% endfor %}

    <div class="callout green">
      <p>{{ article.historical_callout|safe }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">🔍</span>이 브리핑에 나온 용어들</h2>
    <div class="gloss-box">
      <h3>모르는 용어가 있었나요?</h3>
      <div class="gloss-terms">
{% for term in article.glossary_terms %}
        <span class="gloss-term">{{ term }}</span>
{% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--td);margin-bottom:0;">생소한 용어는 용어집에서 쉽게 풀어서 설명해드려요 👇</p>
      <a class="gloss-link" href="glossary.html">📖 투자 용어집 바로가기 →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec">
    <h2><span class="icon">🧭</span>일반 투자자는 어떻게?</h2>
{% for paragraph in article.investor_guide.paragraphs %}
    <p>{{ paragraph|safe }}</p>
{% endfor %}
    <ul style="padding-left:20px;margin:8px 0 14px">
{% for item in article.investor_guide.checklist %}
      <li style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--t);line-height:1.9">{{ item|safe }}</li>
{% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <div class="callout red">
      <p>{{ article.investor_guide.warning|safe }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-footer">
    <a class="nav-btn primary" href="glossary.html">📖 용어집</a>
    <a class="nav-btn" href="index.html">← 리포트 보관함</a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="disclaimer">
      ⚠️ 이 브리핑은 <strong>정보 공유 목적</strong>이며 투자 권유나 특정 종목 추천이 아닙니다.<br>
      투자 결정과 그에 따른 결과는 각자의 판단과 책임하에 이뤄집니다.
    </div>
    <p>💎 AI SYNC 재테크클럽 · AI가 분석한 매일의 시장 브리핑</p>
    <p style="margin-top:4px;">궁금한 용어나 내용은 단톡방에 남겨주세요</p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
